# Folder Structure

## Main Directories
- **src/app**: Next.js app router pages and API routes
- **src/components**: Reusable UI components
  - **layout**: Layout components (headers, footers, etc.)
  - **search**: Search-specific components
  - **ui**: Generic UI components
- **src/hooks**: Custom React hooks
- **src/lib**: Utility functions and shared logic
- **src/types**: TypeScript type definitions
- **public**: Static assets
- **supabase**: Database migrations and configuration

## API Routes
- **/api/crexi**: Endpoints for interacting with Crexi's services
  - **/generate-url**: Generates URLs for Crexi searches
  - **/get-place-id**: Retrieves place IDs for location queries
  - **/property-fit**: Property matching and filtering
  - **/record-search**: Records user search history
- **/api/webhooks**: External service webhook handlers
  - **/clerk**: Authentication webhook handlers

## Authentication
- **sign-in/[[...sign-in]]**: Sign-in pages (Clerk integration)
- **sign-up/[[...sign-up]]**: Sign-up pages (Clerk integration)

## Configuration Files
- **next.config.ts**: Next.js configuration
- **package.json**: NPM dependencies and scripts
- **tsconfig.json**: TypeScript compiler options
- **components.json**: UI component configurations
